title: DDFP 390: Cam Newton vs. Andrew Luck & Week 3 recap
itunes:title: DDFP 390: Cam Newton vs. Andrew Luck & Week 3 recap
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank, Ike Taylor and Maurice Jones-Drew to discuss the biggest stories from Week 3 of the NFL season. Shek is then joined by Gregg Rosenthal and Dan Hanzus to recap Monday Night Football and review the league's top quarterbacks.
